projects.name: New York Airbnb price analysis
projects.description: In this project, I utilized R programming to conduct a comprehensive analysis of Airbnb listings in New York. Leveraging the power of R, I delved into the extensive dataset, exploring factors such as pricing trends, occupancy rates, and geographical distribution of listings. Through the application of statistical techniques and data visualization tools available in R, I gained valuable insights into the dynamics of the Airbnb market in New York. The utilization of R's robust capabilities allowed for in-depth analysis, providing a thorough understanding of the influential factors shaping the Airbnb landscape in this vibrant city.

projects.name: Analysis on IPL Matches
projects.description: In this project, I embarked on a comprehensive analysis of the Indian Premier League (IPL) dataset using SQL, alongside potentially leveraging other tools. By diving into the intricate web of IPL data, I explored various dimensions such as player performance, team statistics, match outcomes, and trends over multiple seasons. Through the lens of SQL, I unearthed meaningful insights, dissecting player stats, match dynamics, and team strategies. The utilization of SQL's querying capabilities enabled me to extract, manipulate, and analyze large datasets efficiently, ultimately leading to valuable conclusions and a deeper understanding of the nuances within the dynamic world of IPL cricket.
